--- linux-2.5.44/arch/i386/kernel/multiring.c	1970-01-01 01:00:00.000000000 +0100
+++ linux-2.5.44_multiring/arch/i386/kernel/multiring.c	2002-10-27 03:18:02.000000000 +0100
